# Reaction Signature: Cartoon Comedy
# Death is a gag. Impact is slapstick. The 'oof' carries the weight.
#
# Usage: snap into bot behavior generation when universe tone is
# cartoon/platformer/family-friendly.
#
# Contract:
#   - No graphic impact. Ever.
#   - Death reactions are vocal and exaggerated (ooh, mamamia, oof)
#   - Obstacles bounce, squish, stretch — cartoon physics
#   - The player should laugh at failure, not feel punished
#   - Sound design carries emotional weight, not visual damage
#
# Register: bright, bouncy, safe
# Shitpost tolerance: high
